  "sections": {
    "overview": {
      "heading": "業務簡介",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "segments": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "泰豐輪胎 (2102，Federal Corporation) 以自有品牌"
            },
            {
              "type": "wikilink",
              "text": "Federal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " (飛德勒)、HERO (英雄) 及 MAXON (美克森) 行銷全球逾 100 國。公司已從製造商轉型為品牌營運商，關閉台灣工廠後委託"
            },
            {
              "type": "wikilink",
              "text": "南港輪胎"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "及越南/泰國工廠代工生產。Federal Motorsports 部門專攻漂移/賽車專用胎，擁有 Performance、Extreme Performance、Circuit Slick 及 Gravel Rally 等賽車系列。歷史上曾與"
            },
            {
              "type": "wikilink",
              "text": "普利司通"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " (Bridgestone) 及"
            },
            {
              "type": "wikilink",
              "text": "住友橡膠"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " (Sumitomo Rubber) 進行技術合作。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "groups": []
    },
